  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'After completing your last challenge in space, you return to the ATLAS
    map to choose your next adventure. Now that you have learned to control the spacecraft,
    it is time to continue exploring the universe. Your spacecraft rises smoothly,
    leaving the space station behind and moving deeper into the vastness of space.
    Stars shine all around, and the journey feels exciting and new.


    The flight
    is calm, giving you time to enjoy the view and prepare for what lies ahead. As
    you travel, you guide the spacecraft carefully, making small adjustments to stay
    on course. You practice steering through space, using everything you learned
    from the previous challenges to navigate safely.


    After traveling through
    the endless darkness of space, you finally arrive at the next destination, a
    space station. Your spacecraft lands safely, and you step inside, ready for the
    next mission.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
