  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "After successfully assembling your hovercraft in the hangar and carefully
    measuring and aligning its parts, you are ready for your first real challenge
    in ATLAS. \n\nIn the challenge you start by using your hovercraft across the
    wide desert plains of ATLAS. This first challenge teaches you how 1D and 2D motion
    work together. By adjusting initial velocity, gravity, and launch speed, you
    learn how timing, force, and trajectory affect your path. Each successful launch
    and landing builds your skill and confidence.\n\nAfter mastering the hovercraft,
    you will drive across the same desert plains. The open terrain challenges every
    turn and maneuver, helping you understand how speed, direction, and timing affect
    motion on the ground.\n\nMastering both hovercraft flight and car driving in
    the desert brings you closer to completing your vehicle and escaping the map
    of ATLAS."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -4890204404628985631, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
