  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Your spacecraft vehicle is out of fuel, so you equip a submarine vehicle
    to explore the depths of the water planet. Pressure and buoyancy constantly test
    your control.


    The challenge is the component buoyancy test. You adjust
    the mass and volume of each component to see how it affects floating and sinking.


    Next
    comes the deep mining mission. You must collect 10 crystals scattered through
    the water. To reach them safely, you carefully add or release air inside the
    submarine to control depth, using your understanding of buoyancy and fluid mechanics.


    By
    successfully balancing components and collecting all crystals, you restore fuel
    and skillfully pilot your submarine back to the surface, ready to continue your
    adventure in Atlas.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
